snippet.title: F.E.A.R. 2 Gameplay (HD)
snippet.description:
Freaky moments from F.E.A.R. 2 Project Origins . 

Danger : Turn your volume a little bit DOWN !

All video options at Maximum / FSAA  4x / Antistropic Filtering 8x / Recorded @ 1280x720 (720p)

CPU : AMD Phenom X4 9850 Black Edition @ 2.5 Ghz (Stock)
RAM : 4 GB Dual Channel DDR2-1066 (Kingmax Semiconductor)
GPU : ATI Radeon Sapphire HD3870 (512 MB GDDR4/256 bit)
Chipset : AMD 780G (Spider Platform - Hybrid CrossFireX) 
Audio : M-Audio Revolution 7.1 HD

Sorry for the sound , I forgot to take the gain out a little bit .
